# Plan Preview & Feedback

## After creating a plan

When you finish creating a plan, tell the user they can preview and share it:

```
Run `cursor-plan-preview share-plan` to preview and share this plan with your team.
```

## Before implementing a plan

When you are about to build from a plan (e.g. the user says "go", "build it", "start"), first check if a file named `<plan-name>-feedback.md` exists in `~/.cursor/plans/` or `.cursor/plans/` in the workspace.

If a feedback file exists:
1. Read it
2. Summarize the feedback to the user
3. Ask if they want to incorporate it before building
